bury |publisher=[[Clarendon Press]] |location=Oxford |isbn=0-19-822235-1 |ref=C7 |url-access=registration |url=https://archive.org/details/lettersoflanfran0000lanf }}\n*{{cite web |year=n.d. |url=http://www.bl.uk/manuscripts/FullDisplay.aspx?ref=Cotton_MS_julius_a_vii |title=Cotton MS Julius A VII |website=[[British Library]] |accessdate=8 November 2014 |ref=C8 }}\n*{{cite book |author=DB |authorlink=Thomas Chatterton |year=1769 |chapter=Godred Crovan. A Poem. Composed by Dopnal Syrric, Scheld of Godred Crovan, King of the Isle of Man |title=Town and Country Magazine |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=qjI3AAAAYAAJ |publisher=A. Hamilton |location=London |pages=425\u2013428 |ref=D12 }}\n*{{cite journal |year=1931 |editor-last=Dobbs |editor-first=ME |title=The Ban-Shenchus |url=http://catalogue.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/cb34418441f |journal=[[Revue Celtique]] |volume=48 |pages=163\u2013234 |ref=D13 }}\n*{{cite book |year=n.d. |editor1-last=Elrington |editor1-first=CR |editor1-link=Charles Richard Elrington |editor2-last=Todd |editor2-first=JH |editor2-link=James Henthorn Todd |title=The Whole Works of the Most Rev. James Ussher, D.D., Lord Archbishop of Armagh, and Primate of All Ireland |url=https://archive.org/details/lifeofjamesusshe04elriuoft |volume=4 |publisher=Hodges and Smith |location=Dublin |ref=E1 }}\n*{{cite book |year=1990 |editor-last=Evans |editor-first=DS |title=A Mediaeval Prince of Wales: The Life of Gruffudd ap Cynan |publisher=Llanerch Enterprises |location= |isbn=0947992472 |ref=E3 }}\n*{{cite book |year=1854 |editor-last=Forester |editor-first=T |title=The Ecclesiastical History of England and Normandy, by Ordericus Vitalus |url=https://archive.org/details/ecclesiasticalhi02ordeuoft |series=[[Bohn's Antiquarian Library]] |volume=2 |publisher=[[Henry G. Bohn]] |location=London |ref=F3 }}\n*{{cite book |year=1883 |editor-last=Gill |editor-first=JF |title=The Statutes of the Isle of Man |volume=1 |url=https://archive.org/details/statutesisleman00mangoog