orov]] {{goal|22}}<br />Stojanovski {{goal|70}}\n|goals2 = \n|stadium = [[Philip II Arena|Gradski stadion]], [[Skopje]] }}\n----\n{{footballbox\n|date = 8 June 2008\n|time = 16:30 [[Central European Summer Time|CEST]]\n|team1 = [[KF Bashkimi (1947\u20132008)|Bashkimi]]\n|score = 4 \u2013 1\n|team2 = [[FK Miravci|Miravci]]\n|goals1 = Ismaili {{goal}}<br />[[Jovica Traj\u010dev|Trajchev]] {{goal}}<br />[[Predrag \u017divadinovi\u0107|\u017divadinovi\u0107]] {{goal}}<br />\u0110orovi\u0107 {{goal}}\n|goals2 = Karakamishev {{goal}}\n|stadium = [[Stadion Tumbe Kafe]], [[Bitola]]\n}}\n\n==Relegation playoff==\n{{footballbox\n|date = 7 June 2008\n|time = 16:30 ([[UTC+2]])\n|team1 = [[FK Lokomotiva Skopje|Lokomotiva]]\n|score = 2 \u2013 2\n|team2 = [[FK Osogovo|Osogovo]]\n|penalties1 =\n|penaltyscore = 3 \u2013 2\n|penalties2 =\n|stadium = [[Gradski Stadion Kavadarci|Gradski stadion]], [[Kavadarci]]\n}}\n----\n{{footballbox\n|date = 7 June 2008\n|time = 16:30 ([[UTC+2]])\n|team1 = [[FK Lepenec|Lepenec]]\n|score = 1 \u2013 2\n|team2 = [[FK Novaci|Novaci 2005]]\n|stadium = [[Stadion Mladost, Strumica|Stadion Mladost]], [[Strumica]]\n}}\n----\n{{footballbox\n|date = 7 June 2008\n|time = 16:30 ([[UTC+2]])\n|team1 = [[FK Ko\u017euf|Kozhuf]]\n|score = 3 \u2013 1\n|team2 = [[FK Ljuboten|Ljuboten]]\n|stadium = [[Stadion Goce Del\u010dev|Stadion Goce Delchev]], [[Prilep]]\n}}\n\n==See also==\n*[[2007\u201308 Macedonian Football Cup]]\n*[[2007\u201308 Macedonian First Football League]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://ffm.mk/ Football Federation of Macedonia]\n*[http://www.macedonianfootball.com MacedonianFootball.com]\n\n{{Macedonian Second Football League seasons}}\n{{2007\u201308 in Republic of Macedonia football}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:2007-08 Second Macedonian Football League}}\n[[Category:2007\u201308 in European second tier association football leagues|Macedonia 2]]\n[[Category:2007\u201308 in Republic of Macedonia football|2]]\n[[Category:Macedonian S